Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:33.97,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(464.857,119.906)\fad(1900,1900)}Mushishi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:44.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go near that fire, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:15.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had I been mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:23.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I have done what that man said?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:29.98,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.22,0:01:29.98,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\be1}The Journey to the Field of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard there's a Mushi-shi in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's talking about Yahagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:01.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's in the fields with Dad and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:04.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,These weird weeds started growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're killing all the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to cut down all the trees around the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:27.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hurt yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought a guest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:37.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have noticed just one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:45.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though you'd have to notice that they're\NMushi with so many of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard there's a new variety around\Nhere, so I figured I'd investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The investigation is already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd heard the name Yahagi somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've read a few of your reports before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never thought you'd be such a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your research on that Mushi must be good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At what I have so far, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:38.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you said you were finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to investigate anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're burning the whole mountain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're burning the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:55.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? I thought it was just the weeds that were bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are all the animals going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We drove out as many of them as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:10.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let those weeds live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain and even your lives will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our last stand for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there really no other options?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what happened so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:05:01.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were tilling the soil to plant crops in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when we found a huge, black rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being so close to a volcano, there\Nare a lot of lava rocks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:14.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As always we just dug it up and\Nleft it at the edge of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:22.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a weed growing from a crack in the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, we didn't even notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went back three days later after a long storm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:39.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the weeds had filled all of the newly tilled soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:45.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cut them and pulled them, but they must\Nhave been connected at the roots...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They kept growing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:54.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was too late by the time I noticed\Nit involved the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weeds began emitting a poison\Nfrom their flower-like attachments
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and killing all of the nearby plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tried everything to exterminate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but nothing worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weeds grew all over the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's approaching the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the whole mountain is too much to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know what the Mushi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what sort of repercussions there'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to do everything you can to gather\Nenough people to pull out every single weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't survive the winter if we lose our crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our lives are at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that it's worth some lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to risk only your own lives, if any.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the frightened villagers would never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So such reasoning holds no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're upset having not noticed the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can't let yourself be intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:24.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to protect my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For that I won't make any compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can have those reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you find them useful for future research.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, be on your way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They cut down the big cinnamon tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms are gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:02.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop cutting, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:13.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much are you putting on\Nthe line for just your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, calm down and think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't want to ruin the mountain either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But our families' lives are at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a Mushi-shi from outside, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:34.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already have a good Mushi-shi here.\NWhat would an outsider know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:39.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As an outsider, you all look like a bunch\Nof panicking monkeys to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lost in your own fear, wailing your arms around blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:50.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're any different from the monkeys,\Nprove it by overcoming your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why man learned to use fire, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our use of fire is part of our intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to be on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the weeds at the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to set fire to the forest tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure enough, she's done a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must regret having to burn it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to you to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:07.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That thing was living inside a lava rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can't give it fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can survive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all gone now though, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let those flames near the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:39.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close all of your containers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone in your neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up or those fireballs are going to infest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do as he says. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those things look like flames, but they're called Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They show up on rainy days and on cold days
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,while they slowly consume the heat of those\Nwho go near expecting it to be fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:15.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On warm days, they hide in tight\Nspaces like pots and hollow logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be a few already lurking in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, be careful when you go near fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:30.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might freeze to death if you're near it for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to be careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a fire is cooler than it should\Nbe, it's probably a Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In every Kagebi is a Mushi called a "Hidane".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Mushi is the heart of the Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They thrive on human heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you're careful, you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought that those\Nweeds were young Hidane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can respond to Hidane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've read about it in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad they weren't a new species, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we found out what it was though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagebi are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one in this village\Nthat can deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it gets out of hand, write me a letter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's for the reports you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take it all upon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll start a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn thing won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Embers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure is cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room just isn't warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like the weeds are all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They shouldn't spawn anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it's just the Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My child's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandpa too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My neighbors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a lot more people got sick after\Neating food cooked on Kagebi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:45.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,as if they got frostbite in their gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:50.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I've taken your warning well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are things now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:17:00.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sick ones should recover with enough rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's become cautious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no new victims for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the Kagebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've vanished since we killed the Hidane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should mostly be gone by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kill the Mushi and the fire burns out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the records say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:27.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I found a mode of life that\Nisn't written in the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:34.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When one consumes enough heat\Nand lives its full lifespan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,those weeds are born again from its remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what you needed my help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can handle that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:52.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just need to go somewhere where there are no people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I breathed in a Kagebi when we\Nwere burning the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human bodies can be containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was inside me slowly consuming my body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:12.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was freezing the whole\Ntime, but that's stopped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, I've started coughing up weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hidane is sprouting in my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's begun secreting poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already told everyone that I\Nwon't be here for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:37.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I intend to leave the village and find\Na place to die before I'm overtaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I want to leave the village to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:48.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I trust you not to make such a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:56.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I could have said what\Nyou just did if I were in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a battle that you people started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not ending any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just end it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catch a Kagebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that going to cure Yahagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hidane are clever, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:44.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their poison must have been something\Nthey just happened to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that poison also causes man to set fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once they have access to fire and they reach maturation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they use the fire to attract people\Nand consume their heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:59.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, the only species to use fire, are\Nin turn being used by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this fire isn't real, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:09.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you provide a larva with a false\Nfire, do you think it can mature?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps to terminate the weeds, we\Nneed to burn them using Kagebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:21.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And food cooked on a Kagebi seems\Nto have the same effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And burn my own gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:31.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I ate some too, and it hurt like it was burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:33.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cure yourself slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Slowly and surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:35.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She continued to live expelling weeds, burning her gut,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:42.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and protecting her village from the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many Kagebi these days, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe because it's getting warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:56.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling where they're still hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's flying towards the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably searching for a cold place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:22.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there it'll lie and wait for winter to come.
